// AS3 linkage class `ScreenClearSave` is the openfl-swf generated library symbol `Screen_clearSave` (the SWF symbol's
// library name was snake/lowerCamel; openfl names the class from it, not the AS3 linkage). Alias the
// two so `new ScreenClearSave()` constructs the real clip (with its named child instances), not an empty stub.
typedef ScreenClearSave = Screen_clearSave;
